      "`DOUBLE_CLICK` VS Code",
      "`CLICK` 'File' in the menu",
      "`CLICK` 'Preferences'",
      "`CLICK` 'Settings'",
      "`CLICK` search bar",
      "`TYPING` 'editor.wordWrapColumn' in the search bar",
      "`CLICK` the 'Editor: Word Wrap Column' setting",
      "`ENTER` '50' in the value field for this setting"
